23
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,440
Has the elderly lady

24
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:03,480
been suffering from insomnia

25
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,120
and anxiety recently?

26
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,640
I just found out about this myself.

27
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,639
I think

28
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,600
it might be because

29
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,730
her child was taken away by the father.

30
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:18,730
I still feel something is strange about this.

31
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,800
So the old man was cooking inside.

32
